From 9a1098e55b9f4a88283e990fae9a84a196627e94 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mira <mira@local>
Date: Wed, 20 May 2026 11:15:55 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] fix(round3): Bug A AI inline action whitelist + Bug B bulk
 drag before/after + Bug C serialize bulk-move
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- aiActions.ts: add kindToBackendAction(kind) mapping rewrite/translate to themselves,
  convert-to-table → rewrite, custom → ask, unknown → ask. Backend schemas.py
  Literal(['continue','expand','summarize','rewrite','translate','outline','ask','search'])
  rejected the prior hardcoded action: 'inline' with 422.
- NovaBlockEditor.tsx runAIInline: action: 'inline' → action: kindToBackendAction(kind).
- SidebarTree.tsx handleMove: drop position==='into' restriction; multi-select drop
  on root sibling at before/after now dispatches onNodesBulkMove with parentId derived
  from target node's parent (null for root siblings) — fixes 'move-out only moves one'.
- bulkMove.ts (new): bulkMoveSerially(api, ids, parent, sortKeys) — serial await,
  merge server responses, per-item failures don't abort batch.
- App.tsx handleNodesBulkMove: replace Promise.all with bulkMoveSerially + merge
  server-returned notes into store. Fixes 'multi-select move-IN appears then vanishes':
  chokidar vault-watcher reload during a half-committed Promise.all read partial state.
- Tests: round3.bugs.test.tsx (Bug B + Bug C), aiActions.bugA.test.ts (Bug A).
  Sandbox: vitest 453 passed (1 file EAGAIN env-only), tsc clean, vite build 3.17s.
